#. Tag: refpurpose
#: man-extractrc.1.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid "Extract message strings from UI and GUI-RC files"
msgstr "Extrae as mensaxes dos ficheiros UI e GUI-RC."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: man-extractrc.1.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>extractrc</command> <group><option><replaceable>filename</"
"replaceable></option></group>"
msgstr ""
"<command>extractrc</command> <group><option><replaceable>ficheiro</"
"replaceable></option></group>"

#. Tag: title
#: man-extractrc.1.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Descrición"

#. Tag: para
#: man-extractrc.1.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>extractrc</command> finds all text tags and other message strings "
"in the given files and writes the corresponding i18n() calls to standard "
"output so that xgettext can parse them."
msgstr ""
"<command>extractrc</command> atopa todas as marcas de texto e outras cadeas "
"de mensaxe nos ficheiros dados e escribe as chamadas i18n() correspondentes "
"na saída estándar para que xgettext poida procesalas."

#. Tag: para
#: man-extractrc.1.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It understands both (&Qt;/&kde;) <application>designer</application>'s "
"<acronym>UI</acronym> files and &XML; GUI-RC files."
msgstr ""
"Entende tanto os ficheiros <acronym>UI</acronym> de &Qt;/&kde; "
"<application>designer</application> como os ficheiros &XML; GUI-RC."

#. Tag: para
#: man-extractrc.1.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid "This utility is part of the KDE Software Development Kit."
msgstr ""
"Esta utilidade forma parte do equipamento de desenvolvemento de programas de "
"KDE."

